# MEME Suite custom alphabet: Nature publication palette
# Muted, high-contrast colors optimized for print and digital publication.
# Source: nature.txt preset adapted to MEME .alph format.
# Usage:  meme --alph nature_dna.alph <sequences> ...
ALPHABET "DNA Nature" DNA-LIKE
A "Adenine" 009B55 ~ T "Thymine" D62728
C "Cytosine" 0059A3 ~ G "Guanine" E69F00
# Ambiguous symbols
U = T
R = AG
Y = CT
K = GT
M = AC
S = CG
W = AT
B = CGT
D = GAT
H = ACT
V = ACG
N = ACGT
X = ACGT
